OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer joins ITV News'
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston for the
OL,8,FTalking Politics podcast, as the prime
OL,9,Fminister travels to the Gulf following
OL,10,Fthe US-Iran ceasefire
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,13,Ftold ITV News' Talking Politics
OL,14,Fpodcast that Israel is "wrong" to
OL,15,Fcontinue its strikes on Lebanon amid a
OL,16,Fceasefire with Iran, saying it "should
OL,17,Fstop" as a "matter of principle".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FThe exclusive interview with ITV News'
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston is the
OL,8,Fprime minister's first since the
OL,9,Festablishment of a fragile two-week
OL,10,Fceasefire deal made between the US and
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FDespite the deal, Israel has continued
OL,14,Fits strikes on Lebanon - which on
OL,15,FWednesday saw its deadliest day -
OL,16,Fthreatening the stability of the
OL,17,Fceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FIt comes as Israeli Prime Minister
OL,7,FBenjamin Netanyahu said his cabinet
OL,8,Fwill hold talks with Lebanon "as soon
OL,9,Fas possible."
OL,11,FWhen asked whether the strikes were a
OL,12,Fbreach of the ceasefire, the prime
OL,13,Fminister said: "It's hard to say that
OL,14,Fthere is a breach when we haven't all
OL,15,Fgot access to all the details of the
OL,16,Fceasefire.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said that
OL,19,Fa cessation of strikes on Lebanon
OL,20,Fshould be part of the US-Iran
OL,21,Fceasefire agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,F"But let me be really clear about it.
OL,7,FThey're wrong. That shouldn't be
OL,8,Fhappening. That should stop."
OL,10,FStarmer added: "The question isn't a
OL,11,Ftechnical one of whether it's a breach
OL,12,Fof the agreement or not. The question
OL,13,Fis actually a matter of principles."
OL,15,FStarmer also addressed the "reopening"
OL,16,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, a vital
OL,17,Fwaterway which remained effectively
OL,18,Fclosed up until the deal was struck on
OL,19,FTuesday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FIran's deputy foreign minister told
OL,7,FITV News' International Editor Emma
OL,8,FMurphy earlier on Thursday that the
OL,9,FStrait "is open", but the prime
OL,10,Fminister said that needs to be
OL,11,F"tested".
OL,13,F"Our position is 'open means open' for
OL,14,Fsafe navigation. That means toll-free
OL,15,Fnavigation and vessels can get
OL,16,Fthrough."
OL,18,FHowever, Starmer said the world will
OL,19,Fhave to "wait and see" whether the
OL,20,FStrait's opening fully materialises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FReports have suggested that part of
OL,7,Fthe ceasefire agreement could be the
OL,8,Fright for Iran to impose tolls on
OL,9,Fships passing through the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz.
OL,12,F"Some of the discussions in the last
OL,13,Fcouple of days have been, let's see
OL,14,Fwhat happens in two, three, four days.
OL,16,F"That'll begin to be the test. So it's
OL,17,Fnot what people say on day one or day
OL,18,Ftwo."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FThe closure of the Strait has caused
OL,7,Fstock markets to plummet worldwide and
OL,8,Foil prices to sharply increase.
OL,10,FIn the interview, Starmer emphasised
OL,11,Fthe need for increased energy
OL,12,Fresilience and independence, warning
OL,13,Fthat "the impact on our economy" is
OL,14,F"clear to see".
OL,16,F"I'm fed up with the fact that
OL,17,Ffamilies across the country see their
OL,18,Fbills go up and down on energy
OL,19,Fbusinesses bills go up and down on
OL,20,Fenergy because of the actions of Putin
OL,21,For Trump across the world," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FOn Trump's comments
OL,8,FThe ceasefire was forged as a result
OL,9,Fof a deadline US President Donald
OL,10,FTrump imposed on Iran to open the
OL,11,FStrait, or "a whole civilisation will
OL,12,Fdie."
OL,14,FThe prime minister did not go as far
OL,15,Fas condemning the president's
OL,16,Flanguage, but said it was "not
OL,17,Flanguage I would use."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,F"I'm clear that for the United
OL,7,FKingdom, we have our principles, we
OL,8,Fhave our values, we will be guided by
OL,9,Fthem in everything that we do."
OL,11,FIt is these principles that the prime
OL,12,Fminister has echoed for his reasoning
OL,13,Fbehind not joining the war in Iran,
OL,14,Finstead only allowing the US to use
OL,15,FBritish air bases for defensive
OL,16,Factions.
OL,18,F"I'm not going to waver or yield to
OL,19,Fany pressure": Keir Starmer says he
OL,20,Fwon't be pushed into the war despite
OL,21,Fthe criticism his decisions drew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FUK will not be "dragged" in to war
OL,13,FThe Iranian deputy foreign minister,
OL,14,Fhowever, accused the UK of allowing
OL,15,Fthe US to launch B2 bombers for
OL,16,Foffensive strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,FThe prime minister firmly disputed
OL,7,Fthis, saying "our bases will not be
OL,8,Fand are not being used for wider
OL,9,Foffensive and particularly for
OL,10,Foffensive on civilians".
OL,12,F"From the get-go, we've been
OL,13,Fmonitoring this situation. So I'm
OL,14,Fpretty clear in my own mind about what
OL,15,Fwe've agreed and what the use of the
OL,16,Fbases are."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775782987
OL,3,CStarmer: Israel is 'wrong' for
OL,4,Cstriking Lebanon amid Iran ceasefire
OL,6,F"I've been saying we are not going to
OL,7,Fbe dragged into this war because I say
OL,8,Fthere must be a lawful basis. That
OL,9,Fmatters if you're going to commit our
OL,10,Fservice personnel to risk their lives."
OL,12,FThe prime minister will continue to
OL,13,Fmeet Gulf leaders on Thursday, after
OL,14,Falready having met Saudi Crown Prince
OL,15,FMohammed Bin Salman and UAE President
OL,16,FSheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
